{"tid":2295081,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Codecademy自學討論區","createTime":"2020-11-21T13:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T15:23:03.000Z","uid":156068,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"85ee9d3f88c58cc7d66a5f779aae0a7c33f201e9","tid":2295081,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:13:00.000Z","msg":"有無人用緊codecademy自學緊? <br />\n<br />\n而家學緊SQL同Python, 但係完全唔知做緊咩, 剩係識跟指示打d command <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟做曬佢d exercises可唔可以做IT工<br />\n<br />\n利申: 文科人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e65a1aaeebcfb2273c3d11a7190fc88e5409d6","tid":2295081,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:14:08.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98fd35af190878f5c92a8793e930c8e31fd521f","tid":2295081,"uid":6071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"有冇上過cs50 我覺得由呢一個做切入點比較好"},{"pid":"6ca3b3fa4687fd86eb14848fb3dea4f58c4e9768","tid":2295081,"uid":257658,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"85ee9d3f88c58cc7d66a5f779aae0a7c33f201e9","tid":2295081,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:13:00.000Z","msg":"有無人用緊codecademy自學緊? <br />\n<br />\n而家學緊SQL同Python, 但係完全唔知做緊咩, 剩係識跟指示打d command <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟做曬佢d exercises可唔可以做IT工<br />\n<br />\n利申: 文科人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"coding世界, 熟能生巧. 唔會好似DSE考中文咁化學.<br />\n但你要去到業界既標準, 要打真軍先有用. <br />\n<br />\n學就唔好學Python啦, C++ Java 都仲好d. <br />\n我做左年幾Java major CS, 好多野都係唔識.<br />\n<br />\ncode狗不嬲唔夠人做. 你有既貨同你人工成正比. <br />\n<br />\n利申 Java code狗."},{"pid":"544a826a53f800fe2624f0ba6f76495e17b90fcf","tid":2295081,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:37:22.000Z","msg":"自學用codecademy係唔work的，用hyperskill"},{"pid":"ed45133de7619db2b605b829b5104eb3e95c84d2","tid":2295081,"uid":79869,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:10:33.000Z","msg":"codecademy同hyperskill都玩過<br />\n不過就算我有CS底，兩隻都間中有d問題同指示比得唔清晰<br />\n所以你要偷睇其他人既command/solution先過到關<br />\n<br />\n如果你無CS底，但有充足時間同心機<br />\n我會推薦hyperskill，佢有完整既Knowledge Map<br />\n會教返齊你一切CS background knowledge, ie. Data Structure, Algorithm, 甚至數學<br />\n厭step by step悶，佢仲有Project Mode, result orientated<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qizEuti.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqizEuti.png&h=cdcc85ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過呢，如果你有錢肯貨金，對於新手入門，我最推薦既人Code School<br />\n佢拍既教學片係超級超級有趣<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Atlt4S0rABo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAtlt4S0rABo&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5rw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=e1936d12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Atlt4S0rABo</a><br />\n順帶一提，花d心機可以google到佢既開心版resource, 不過就無得玩佢地既interactive course<br />\n<br />\n最後呢其實khanacademy都有電腦course<br />\n其中我超推薦佢既Information theory，d片拍到好似睇緊歷史電影咁<br />\n<br />\n可惜codebabes無SQL同Python course, 無得推薦"},{"pid":"f44365ded8b0378e91753ba5de59a254e370eaed","tid":2295081,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a98fd35af190878f5c92a8793e930c8e31fd521f","tid":2295081,"uid":6071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"